<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>Include &lt;glm/gtc/noise.hpp&gt; to use the features of this extension.</para>

<para>Defines 2D, 3D and 4D procedural noise functions Based on the work of Stefan Gustavson and Ashima Arts on &quot;webgl-noise&quot;: <link xlink:href="https://github.com/ashima/webgl-noise">https://github.com/ashima/webgl-noise</link> Following Stefan Gustavson&apos;s paper &quot;Simplex noise demystified&quot;: <link xlink:href="http://www.itn.liu.se/~stegu/simplexnoise/simplexnoise.pdf">http://www.itn.liu.se/~stegu/simplexnoise/simplexnoise.pdf</link> </para>
</section>
